ISLAMABAD, Jan 28 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Friday thatamong the ten young men who embraced martyrdom in Balochistan, two belonged to Jhelum.
In a tweet, while paying tributes to the martyred army personnel, the minister said graveyards of Jhelum have the fragrance of the blood of such martyrs.
